    {
      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>steak[s]</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Meanwhile, combine your<strong> egg[s]</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> </span><strong>flour</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml] </span>[100ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> in a jug, then whisk in your <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>batter</strong> in the fridge to rest</p><p>Strip your <strong>thyme leaves</strong> from their stalks (discard the stalks), then finely chop the <strong>thyme leaves</strong> and <strong>parsley</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
