    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> with your <strong>horseradish sauce </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> to the bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up, then set aside to marinate</p><p>Add the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to one side of a baking tray (or two!) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 15 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
