    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then chop into thick batons</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing with the side of a knife (keep the skins on!)</p><p>Once the potatoes have had 15 min, add the <strong>carrot</strong> <strong>batons</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to the other side of the tray[s] with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 30 min further or until everything is golden and tender</p>",
