    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested rump steak </strong>finely and pour any <strong>resting juices</strong> from the board into the gravy</p><p>Drizzle your <strong>truffle oil</strong> over the <strong>roast potatoes </strong>– these are your <strong>truffled roasties</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced rump steak</strong> with the <strong>truffled roasties</strong>, <strong>herby</strong> <strong>Yorkshires</strong>, <strong>roasted carrots & garlic </strong>and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to the side, then drizzle the <strong>gravy</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
